OL,3,CHealth issues won't be solved by one
OL,4,Cminister in one term, says Swann
OL,6,FThe Health Minister Robin Swann MLA
OL,7,Fhas confirmed he intends to run for
OL,8,Fparliament in the next Westminster
OL,9,Felection.
OL,11,FMr Swann had been announced as the
OL,12,FUUP's candidate for the South Antrim
OL,13,Fconstituency before the Executive was
OL,14,Frestored and he was reappointed to his
OL,15,Frole as Health Minister.
OL,17,FThe minister also said that the
OL,18,Fdepartment could be facing a deficit
OL,19,Fof up to #1billion.
