OL,3,CHealth issues won't be solved by one
OL,4,Cminister in one term, says Swann
OL,6,FMr Swann further agreed that the NHS
OL,7,Fis "no longer working for everyone".
OL,9,FThere had been speculation in recent
OL,10,Fdays that Mr Swann may step back from
OL,11,Fhis ambition to run for Westminster,
OL,12,Fnow that he has taken up his
OL,13,Fministerial post.
OL,15,FIn an interview with UTV, Mr Swann
OL,16,Fmade clear that he is "still running
OL,17,Ffor Westminster in South Antrim". He
OL,18,Ffurther said that parties had changed
OL,19,Fministers during terms previously.
