OL,3,CHealth issues won't be solved by one
OL,4,Cminister in one term, says Swann
OL,6,F"The problems that we have in health
OL,7,Fwon't be solved by one minister, nor
OL,8,Fin one term.
OL,10,F"I think it's strange to suggest that
OL,11,Fpoliticians don't run in elections,
OL,12,Fit's what we do, it's what all
OL,13,Fpoliticians do.
OL,15,F"I actually think there would be an
OL,16,Fadvantage if I was an MP in
OL,17,FWestminster, bringing the knowledge
OL,18,Fthat I have as health minister into
OL,19,FWestminster.
