OL,3,CHealth issues won't be solved by one
OL,4,Cminister in one term, says Swann
OL,6,F"I can make sure that the health
OL,7,Fservice in Northern Ireland is
OL,8,Factually being understood and focused
OL,9,Fon on Westminster, rather than a
OL,10,Fforgotten part, which we can often
OL,11,Fseem to be."
OL,13,FThis is the second time the UUP MLA
OL,14,Fhas held the post of health minister.
OL,16,FHe previously held the brief from 2020
OL,17,Fto 2022, overseeing the department's
OL,18,Fresponse to the Covid-19 pandemic.
