OL,3,CHealth issues won't be solved by one
OL,4,Cminister in one term, says Swann
OL,6,FHis in-tray looks similarly daunting
OL,7,Fthis time around, not least in trying
OL,8,Fto resolve the pay disputes that have
OL,9,Fled to strikes across the health
OL,10,Fservice here in recent months.
OL,12,FMr Swann said the department is in
OL,13,Fnegotiations with its staff on
OL,14,Fresolving the public sector pay
OL,15,Fdispute which has seen strike action
OL,16,Facross the health service.
OL,18,F"It's almost a deja vu. When I came
OL,19,Finto this post back in January 2020
OL,20,Fthere was industrial action.
