OL,3,CHealth issues won't be solved by one
OL,4,Cminister in one term, says Swann
OL,6,F"Now, we have that wider piece of
OL,7,Findustrial action.
OL,9,F"There's a real Executive commitment
OL,10,Facross all departments and across all
OL,11,Fparties to get this issue resolved.
OL,13,F"But it will take work from an
OL,14,FExecutive point of view to make sure
OL,15,Fthe finances are in place."
OL,17,FThe public sector pay awards are
OL,18,Fcomplicated by the Department of
OL,19,FHealth's budgetary pressures.
