OL,3,CHealth issues won't be solved by one
OL,4,Cminister in one term, says Swann
OL,6,FMr Swann estimated in the interview
OL,7,Fthat the department could be facing a
OL,8,Fdeficit of up to #1billion.
OL,10,F"That's a massive number. But that
OL,11,Ftakes account of the monies that we
OL,12,Fneed to take care of this year's pay
OL,13,Fsettlement, that we give a pay award
OL,14,Fnext year.
OL,16,F"And also those recurring pressures
OL,17,Fthat we see across health and social
OL,18,Fcare, just in the normal day-to-day
OL,19,Frunning."
